ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"繼續狙擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336eb075042a76d859e887439ba5387bd126c335","tid":2493824,"uid":68261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1362ee3e1d8bb6d68fccd8d933ead730fbf1794","tid":2493824,"uid":33028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c51236cf28bbc975066fce994f9c60d1d0e17483","tid":2493824,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27c94eb1a3108e828c2dad2aa9755bd38e2cf4e1","tid":2493824,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27300ecc29a2114a16f480da33683f6601fd862d","tid":2493824,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"點解阿布泰接到舉報就調查 <br />\n360就唔撚關海關事嘅？<br />\n<br />\n香港海關於連鎖零售店集團檢獲逾八千八百件懷疑違規沐浴露及家居清潔用品（附圖）<br />\n<br />\n2021年4月9日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港海關昨日（四月八日）於一間連鎖零售店集團多個處所檢獲十四款合共八千八百○五件懷疑違規沐浴露、家居清潔劑和衣物漂白劑，涉案貨品包裝上的產品資料均沒有標示中文及英文的雙語警告或警誡字句，涉嫌違反《消費品安全條例》（《條例》）的附屬法例《消費品安全規例》（《規例》）。行動中檢獲產品估計市值共約四十萬元，一人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">海關早前接獲舉報，指一間連鎖零售店集團位於荃灣和沙田的零售店鋪有多款懷疑違規家居清潔劑出售。海關人員隨即進行調查，</span></strong></span>從六間分別位於金鐘、鰂魚涌、旺角、荃灣和沙田的零售店鋪試購涉案共十四款產品。<br />\n<br />\n經調查後，海關發現該些產品包裝上的產品資料沒有標示就安全存放、使用、耗用或處置的中文警告或警誡字句，當中十二款只附有泰文警告或警誡字句，而另外兩款產品則只附有泰文及英文警告或警誡字句。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.customs.gov.hk/tc/publication_press/press/index_id_3178.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.customs.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublication_press%2Fpress%2Findex_id_3178.html&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=09e459be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.customs.gov.hk/tc/publication_press/press/index_id_3178.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"阿布泰都唔係拉佢食物標籤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"涉案貨品包裝上的產品資料均沒有標示中文及英文的雙語警告或警誡字句，涉嫌違反《消費品安全條例》（《條例》）的附屬法例《消費品安全規例》（《規例》）。行動中檢獲產品估計市值共約四十萬元，一人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap456&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=64ed106b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap456</a><br />\n《消費品安全條例》<br />\n消費品 (consumer goods)指一般供應予私人使用或耗用而非附表所列的貨品，並包括供應該等貨品時所用的包裝；<br />\n附表<br />\n[第2條]<br />\n下列物品並非本條例第2條所指的消費品 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)<span class=\"red\">食物及水</span>；<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食物標籤係另一條法例，唔係海關管<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cfs.gov.hk/tc_chi/faq/faq_03.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfs.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Ffaq%2Ffaq_03.html&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=fbbe1274\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cfs.gov.hk/tc_chi/faq/faq_03.html</a>"},{"pid":"ff00f8fa7cf2817a0279bb38f5a915bbd8e49706","tid":2493824,"uid":33028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5e9d4daf3bb93627b857cdae10b78992569cf30c","tid":2493824,"uid":63287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:24:15.000Z","msg":"關食環撚事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:35:13.000Z","msg":"食物標籤係食物環境衞生署食物安全中心執法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/news/details/20171011_1154.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fnews%2Fdetails%2F20171011_1154.html&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=10b7bbe3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/news/details/20171011_1154.html</a>"},{"pid":"3c8bbd4a339123c5a96c416bca5675d739b6aba8","tid":2493824,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1362ee3e1d8bb6d68fccd8d933ead730fbf1794","tid":2493824,"uid":33028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c51236cf28bbc975066fce994f9c60d1d0e17483","tid":2493824,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27c94eb1a3108e828c2dad2aa9755bd38e2cf4e1","tid":2493824,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"阿布泰都唔係拉佢食物標籤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"涉案貨品包裝上的產品資料均沒有標示中文及英文的雙語警告或警誡字句，涉嫌違反《消費品安全條例》（《條例》）的附屬法例《消費品安全規例》（《規例》）。行動中檢獲產品估計市值共約四十萬元，一人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap456&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=64ed106b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap456</a><br />\n《消費品安全條例》<br />\n消費品 (consumer goods)指一般供應予私人使用或耗用而非附表所列的貨品，並包括供應該等貨品時所用的包裝；<br />\n附表<br />\n[第2條]<br />\n下列物品並非本條例第2條所指的消費品 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)<span class=\"red\">食物及水</span>；<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食物標籤係另一條法例，唔係海關管<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cfs.gov.hk/tc_chi/faq/faq_03.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfs.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Ffaq%2Ffaq_03.html&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=fbbe1274\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cfs.gov.hk/tc_chi/faq/faq_03.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"yes, 食物係食環<br />\n食物標籤就可以中或英, 但食用限期<span class=\"red\"><strong>必須同時</strong></span>有中同英"},{"pid":"8a82fba4a27ca0ddbc82c95d948b454473d534c5","tid":2493824,"uid":48083,